{"tid":1755444,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"你地班連登仔唔好再FF了","createTime":"2019-11-25T14:54:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T15:00:20.000Z","uid":7292,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f801a39c2056dd6b00521ddb85e882755317231b","tid":1755444,"uid":7292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T14:54:16.000Z","msg":"仆你個街，近排連登開始有個風向：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">林鄭其實係幕後大功臣，政治智慧遠超常人，冇佢香港都唔會connect成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n我又想問下你地究竟<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">瞓撚醒未？</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n林鄭呢條大仆街從政咁多年，要清算佢既惡政一大堆：<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>1.皇后碼頭照拆，但保育走數</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>2.囍帖街暫緩後繼續拆晒，屌你老母死政棍</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>3.政改與學生對話，事後清算</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母啦！佢係有心connect香港既需要先破除香港地標、學生前途，而後立佢既特首之路？<br />\n<br />\n係呀我相信人性有光輝既一面，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">但呢條柒婆一定係人性最黑暗既仆街冚家剷</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n屌，咪撚再FF啦你地<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>光復香港，時代革命</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n呢句口號只會靠<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我地</span></strong></span>先成功，而唔係靠林鄭條仆街冚家剷！"},{"pid":"0c705a43f98da372b0e4904a05fcd19c67ad834b","tid":1755444,"uid":7292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T14:55:10.000Z","msg":"求下你地唔好再FF了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好將功勞歸於敵人"},{"pid":"714e9560338b7a4713739c31f20fff2b67857c1a","tid":1755444,"uid":7292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T14:55:35.000Z","msg":"求下你地唔好再FF了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好將功勞歸於敵人"},{"pid":"980ea5971996f81a49fa0551d504bc2bc919f44a","tid":1755444,"uid":7292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T14:55:59.000Z","msg":"求下你地唔好再FF了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好將功勞歸於敵人"},{"pid":"2a8c6692a75bf28f00480cb18e51172a6a6f0fde","tid":1755444,"uid":303297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T14:56:05.000Z","msg":"感覺似玩膠多D"},{"pid":"80dc629410e7af486804673ff7d17cfc52b65c6a","tid":1755444,"uid":7292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T14:56:12.000Z","msg":"求下你地唔好再FF了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好將功勞歸於敵人"},{"pid":"a0b7f5f1b236316afbb77821aa5603fa3a347c04","tid":1755444,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T14:56:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fe088d1330a47387f94c4e253d62eb9f660b5811","tid":1755444,"uid":7292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T14:56:33.000Z","msg":"求下你地唔好再FF了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好將功勞歸於敵人"},{"pid":"24bae3e59ecc8c75f4b79ac6f21f72aaba805137","tid":1755444,"uid":235665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T15:00:20.000Z","msg":"贏左區選沾沾自喜又開始玩膠，香港人d劣根性，快樂建築在痛苦上，飲鴆止渴就好開心。"}]}